Senator Dino Melaye representing Kogi West Senatorial district in the National Assembly has called on Nigerians to vote out President Muhammadu Buhari describing him as incompetent.
The 44-years old senator argued that Buhari lacks the necessary skills to govern Nigeria successfully.
Melaye made this known in a video he posted on his Instagram page.
He said “You can’t give what you don’t have. President Muhammadu Buhari is not intellectually, emotionally, physically, mentally equipped to govern this country”
Melaye accompanied the video with “Vote out incompetence! Vote out Buhari”.
